text_zh: 面对新的挑战时，你的第一反应是什么？
text_en: When facing new challenges, what is your first reaction?
option_a_zh: 兴奋地接受挑战，追求突破
option_a_en: Excitedly accept the challenge and pursue breakthroughs
option_b_zh: 仔细评估风险，确保安全
option_b_en: Carefully assess risks to ensure safety
option_d_en: Collaborate with others to tackle it together

text_zh: 什么最能激发你的内在动力？
option_a_en: Gaining recognition and sense of achievement

text_zh: 在做重要决定时，你最依赖什么？
text_en: When making important decisions, what do you rely on most?
What are you most afraid of losing?

text_zh: 什么样的环境让你感到最舒适？
text_en: What kind of environment makes you feel most comfortable?

text_zh: 在团队中，你通常扮演什么角色？
text_en: What role do you usually play in a team?

text_zh: 面对冲突时，你的典型反应是？
text_en: What is your typical reaction when facing conflicts?
option_a_en: Face it directly and seek solutions
option_d_en: Listen to all parties and seek consensus

text_zh: 在工作中，你更喜欢如何与他人互动？
text_en: How do you prefer to interact with others at work?

text_zh: 当需要做出群体决策时，你倾向于？
text_en: When group decisions need to be made, you tend to?
option_a_en: Lead the discussion and decision-making process

text_zh: 在压力情况下，你的表现通常是？
text_en: How do you usually perform under pressure?
